#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
When you view a distributor's record, you will see the following fields (assuming your
account sufficient rights to at least view them):
<ul>
<li><a href="field-Distributor_Name.cgi">Distributor name</a>
<li><a href="field_Distributor_Address.cgi">Address</a>
<li><a href="field_Distributor_Phone.cgi">Phone</a>
<li><a href="field_Distributor_Contact.cgi">Contact</a>
<li><a href="field_Distributor_Bags.cgi">Bags</a>
<li><a href="field_Distributor_Reimbursement.cgi">Reimbursement rates</a>
</ul>
To modify fields you are allowed to modify, click on
<a href="button_Edit.cgi"><button>Edit</button></a>.  Once you have completed any changes,
click on <a href="button-Update.cgi"><button>Update</button></a>.

<p>To create an entirely new set of routes with the current set of patrons and drivers, balanced to
the least driving time for all, click on
<a href="hutton-Rebalance.cgi"><button>Rebalance routes</button></a>.
It is unlikely you have the permissions rights to do this.

<p>Click
<a href="button_Maps.cgi"><button>List maps</button></a>
to view maps of all the routes driven for this distribution center.

<p>Click <a href="button_larr.cgi"><button>&larr;</button></a> to return to a higher menu.

<p>A <a href="search_Route.cgi">summary</a>
(search) of all the routes associated with this distributor is also shown on this page.


